&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;headings&quot;&gt;Headings&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are six levels of headings. They correspond with the six levels of HTML headings. You‚Äôve probably noticed them already in the page. Each level down uses one more hash character. But we are using just 4 of them.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&quot;headings-can-be-small&quot;&gt;Headings can be small&lt;/h1&gt;

